			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_MOREDG_URGENCE_HTA</LocID>											<Text>중증 고혈압</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_MOREDG_URGENCE_HTA_DESCRIPTION</LocID>								<Text>혈압이 급격하고도 심하게 상승했습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_MOREDG_SYNCOPE_REFLEXE</LocID>										<Text>반사성 실신</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_MOREDG_SYNCOPE_REFLEXE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>							<Text>신경학적으로 유도된 혈압이나 심박수 감소로 인한 짧은 의식 상실입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
