			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_MOREDG_FA_ECG</LocID>												<Text>심방세동</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_MOREDG_FA_ECG_DESCRIPTION</LocID>									<Text>AF. 심전도 검사 결과, P파가 관찰되지 않았으며 불규칙한 QRS파가 관찰되었습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
