			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_MOREDG_NPC1_MUTE</LocID>								<Text>NPC1 muté</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_MOREDG_NPC1_MUTE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>					<Text>The proteins NPC1 and NPC2 seem to work at the level of the endo-lysosomal system to facilitate the intracellular transport of cholesterol and other molecules, but their precise function is not yet known.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
